                            <span>Billing & Payments</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #e7f7f0; border: 1px solid #1dbf73; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <i class="fas fa-headset" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #1dbf73;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 style="color: #222325; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Need Immediate Help?</h4>
                    <p style="color: #62646a; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        Our support team is available 24/7 to assist you with any questions or issues.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/chat" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Start Live Chat</a>
